(define (integrand x)
  (let ((dydx (calc/cos x)))
    (calc/sqrt (+ 1 (* dydx dydx)))))

(define arc-length (calc/integral integrand 0 3.14159))

(display \"Arc length of sine wave on [0,π]: \")
(display arc-length)
(newline)
```

<!-- BUILD: run, print. -->

[VISUAL: Console output: `3.820…`]

---

