(define (f x) (/ 1 x))

(define (approx-integral b)
  (calc/integral f 1 b))

(display \"∫₁¹⁰ 1/x: \")
(display (approx-integral 10))
(newline)

(display \"∫₁¹⁰⁰ 1/x: \")
(display (approx-integral 100))
(newline)

(display \"∫₁¹⁰⁰⁰ 1/x: \")
(display (approx-integral 1000))
(newline)
```

<!-- BUILD: run, print. -->

[VISUAL: Console output: 2.302…, 4.605…, 6.907… (ln 10, ln 100, ln 1000—growing without bound).]

---

