(display \"a(100) = \") (display (a 100)) (newline)
(display \"a(1000) = \") (display (a 1000)) (newline)
```

<!-- BUILD: run, print. -->

[VISUAL: Console output: 2.5937…, 2.7048…, 2.7169…—converging to e ≈ 2.71828.]

---

