### Example 61: Taylor series for ln(1+x), x=0.5

```scheme
(define (taylor-ln x n)
  (fold + 0
        (map (lambda (k)
               (let ((sign (expt -1 (+ k 1)))
                     (pow (expt x k)))
                 (/ (* sign pow) k)))
             (iota n 1))))

(define x 0.5)

(display \"ln(1.5), 5 terms: \") (display (taylor-ln x 5)) (newline)
(display \"ln(1.5), 10 terms: \") (display (taylor-ln x 10)) (newline)
(display \"ln(1.5), exact: \") (display (calc/log 1.5)) (newline)
```

