### Example 64: Evaluate the Taylor series at a point

```scheme
(define series (calc/taylor 'exp 0 10))

(define (eval-poly coeffs x)
  (fold + 0
        (map (lambda (c k) (* c (expt x k)))
             coeffs
             (iota (length coeffs) 0))))

(define val (eval-poly series 1.0))

(display \"e^1 from Taylor coeffs: \")
(display val)
(newline)
```

<!-- BUILD: run, print. -->

[VISUAL: Console output: 2.71828…]

